# Working Memory

## Current Focus
What you are working on right now. The indexer ignores this section.

## Recent Sessions
Brief notes per session. The indexer ignores this section.

### Key Decisions
The indexer reads bullet entries from this section. Format:
- One sentence summary of the decision (YYYY-MM-DD)
- Another decision with its date (YYYY-MM-DD)
- Decisions without dates are still indexed but sort to the bottom

### Infrastructure Map
This section is ignored. The indexer stops reading at the next `### ` heading.
